[SPEAKER_01]: In diversity, there is beauty and there is strength.

52
00:05:16,835 --> 00:05:21,536
[SPEAKER_01]: In Medford, there is so much beautiful diversity and strength.

53
00:05:22,297 --> 00:05:28,538
[SPEAKER_01]: I continue to work and support Medford Public Schools' work on race, equity, and diversity across the district.

54
00:05:29,358 --> 00:05:41,637
